VIDEO footage of thugs stealing an ATM and putting it at a
back of a bakkie has surfaced on social media. In the CCTV footage,
over five armed men can be seen grabbing the ATM and loading it onto an Opel
Corsa bakkie. The thugs reportedly fired
shots but no one was injured. The incident reportedly
happened at a supermarket in Lady Frere, in the Eastern Cape on 1 August. 